title: Robot (2010) Action Version - English Subs
description:
STORY:

A human-android constructed by a scientist for military purposes, falls in love with the to-be bride of its creator.

this is the Pyre8Storm version (Action version). The full movie has a lot of singing and dancing in it, which is no 
problem for those who are used to it and like it; for me it's like somebody changed the channel or something, 
so I put together an edited version simply because I love the movie and there is no version like this one that I know of.


Side notes:

This movie has dark theme to it and should be viewd by persons over the age of 15 years.

English subtiles are included (SRT file) so no hard coded subs for those who speak Tamil.
